  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Bars &amp; Restaurants</strong></span></p>
<p><strong>Due Tori Lounge &amp; Restaurant</strong> is located on the ground floor of the hotel in the large lobby beneath its medieval gothic arches. Here you can enjoy a delicious meal amidst beautiful and ornate surroundings. The restaurant serves the finest of traditional Italian cuisine and its gourmet cuisine is recognised by the prestigious French red guide. It has a large selection of wines from the area that is rich in wine growing traditions.</p>
<p><strong>Terrazza Panoramica Grill Restaurant</strong> is set on one of the highest rooftops of Verona and has incredible views over the city. The restaurant specialises in its grilled meats and fish dishes, but also offers a wide selection of cocktails and wines for those who wish to a warm evening aperitif on the large terrace.</p>
<p><strong>The Breakfast Room</strong> is fully equipped with a buffet breakfast each morning with fresh and local products such as freshly made breads, pastries, cereals, yoghurt, meats and cheeses. There’s also a wide choice of teas and coffees available.</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li>Lounge</li>
<li>Library</li>
<li>Courtyard &amp; winter garden</li>
<li>Parking with valet service approx. €30 – payable locally</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
