  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Classic Rooms</strong> are about 20-25m². They are furnished in a luxurious style with authentic period furniture and the walls are adorned with precious tapestries. Each room is individually decorated, some with parquet flooring and other with sumptuous carpets. With pure linen sheets and white cotton satin quilt covers you’ll have a comfortable rejuvenating sleep, ready for a day of exploring Verona’s attractions. All rooms have private bath or shower, air conditioning, television, free wifi, minibar, safe and hairdryer. These rooms sleep two people.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms </strong>are about 25-35m². They sleep up to three people and are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites </strong>are about 35-45m². They sleep up to three people and have tea and coffee making facilities. They are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Suites </strong>are about 55m². They sleep up to three people and have tea and coffee making facilities. They are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Classic and Deluxe Rooms for Single Use </strong>are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
